Hans C. Helmerich



Mr. Hans C. Helmerich is Independent Director at Cimarex Energy Co., Independent Director at Atwood Oceanics, Inc., Chairman at Helmerich & Payne, Inc., and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Helmerich & Payne International Drilling Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Cimarex Energy Co., Atwood Oceanics, Inc., Helmerich & Payne International Drilling Co., and The Northwestern Mutual Life Insurance Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Dartmouth College.



